ed upon\n21-cm emission from HI galaxies by a factor of five to six.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 May 2001 01:19:33 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 15 Jun 2001 18:13:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-06"}
